conify 是一个图标库，提供了多种图标集合的访问和使用方式。",{"type":182,"children":183,"toc":539},"root",[184,192,198,203,208,392,397,406,411,416,421,436,441,446,500,505,510,533],{"type":185,"tag":186,"props":187,"children":189},"element","h2",{"id":188},"简介",[190],{"type":191,"value":188},"text",{"type":185,"tag":193,"props":194,"children":195},"p",{},[196],{"type":191,"value":197},"Iconify 致力于让图标变得更容易使用。",{"type":185,"tag":193,"props":199,"children":200},{},[201],{"type":191,"value":202},"提供了统一的图标开发规范：统一的命名约定，比如 camera-with-flash、home-outlined；统一的颜色规范，分单色和多色图标，单色图标使用 currentColor 作为颜色值，所以默认可以改颜色；统一的资源格式，禁止文本、栅格图片、外部资源、脚本等内容，因为公共的图标库使用 Iconify Tools 工具处理过。",{"type":185,"tag":193,"props":204,"children":205},{},[206],{"type":191,"value":207},"以前使用 Iconfont 时，设计师在网站手动上传图标时是不会转换为自动颜色的，即颜色被硬编码到了图标文件中：",{"type":185,"tag":209,"props":210,"children":214},"pre",{"className":211,"code":212,"language":213,"meta":178,"style":178},"language-html shiki shiki-themes material-theme-lighter github-light github-dark monokai","\u003Csvg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n  \u003Cpath fill=\"blue\" d=\"M5 5h14v14H5z\"/>\n\u003C/svg>\n","html",[215],{"type":185,"tag":216,"props":217,"children":218},"code",{"__ignoreMap":178},[219,312,375],{"type":185,"tag":220,"props":221,"children":224},"span",{"class":222,"line":223},"line",1,[225,231,237,243,248,254,260,264,269,273,277,281,285,290,294,298,303,307],{"type":185,"tag":220,"props":226,"children":228},{"style":227},"--shiki-light:#39ADB5;--shiki-default:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;--shiki-sepia:#F8F8F2",[229],{"type":191,"value":230},"\u003C",{"type":185,"tag":220,"props":232,"children":234},{"style":233},"--shiki-light:#E53935;--shiki-default:#22863A;--shiki-dark:#85E89D;--shiki-sepia:#F92672",[235],{"type":191,"value":236},"svg",{"type":185,"tag":220,"props":238,"children":240},{"style":239},"--shiki-light:#9C3EDA;--shiki-default:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0;--shiki-sepia:#A6E22E",[241],{"type":191,"value":242}," width",{"type":185,"tag":220,"p